      <div class="post-341 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-wp tag-37" id="post-341"> 
       <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://help.laoxuehost.com/scripts/wp/wp-anti-spam.html" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to WP Anti Spam 小 1.8">WP Anti Spam 小 1.8</a></h2> 
       <div class="post-meta"> 
        <span class="date">十一月 10th, 2011</span> | 
        <span class="author">老薛主机</span> | 
        <span class="views">19,297 views</span> | 
        <span class="edit"></span> 
        <span class="comments"><a href="http://help.laoxuehost.com/scripts/wp/wp-anti-spam.html#comments">3 个评论 &raquo;</a></span> 
       </div> 
       <div class="entry"> 
        <p>小墙的防spam的能力，可以说100%啊！Akismet有时候会“误杀”正常的评论，而且会浪费数据库，强烈推荐大家使用“小”</p> 
        <p>⑾铝写a copy 到模板的 functions.php<br /> <span id="more-341"></span></p> 
        <div class="wp_syntax" style="position:relative;">
